{"tid":2495854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居神戶大熊貓「旦旦」突患心臟病  或不送回中国","createTime":"2021-04-19T12:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T12:22:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db57096671aa95fcd1f0fd960ec2e3e83918b882","tid":2495854,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:13:19.000Z","msg":"原定送回中國的旅日雌性大熊貓旦旦，由於有心臟病，可能不會送返中國。日本神戶市立王子動物園表示，25歲的旦旦患上心臟病，出現心律不齊、心跳加快的症狀，正接受藥物治療。 <br />\n<br />\n旦旦在今年1月下旬的定期體檢中，驗出有心律不齊等問題，曾一度恢復，但上月復發，暫時不危及性命。園方相信，旦旦患心臟病的成因，是年紀大令運動量及食慾下降，睡眠時間變長。 <br />\n<br />\n旦旦是日方向中國租借，合同去年7月到期，但因疫情而無法安排運送旦旦回國的航班。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/dbb01f50fb3b2ca0f17256d4bb8f8099/2021/04/19b1fe2a4aadeed830299f161759c222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Fdbb01f50fb3b2ca0f17256d4bb8f8099%2F2021%2F04%2F19b1fe2a4aadeed830299f161759c222.jpg&h=cae8b642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：神戶市立王子動物園 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2387933&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=ed247455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387933</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2387933&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=ed247455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387933</a>"},{"pid":"6f41ae9e5ac73a094be7b5587d80cc30e16a6e71","tid":2495854,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.makeameme.org/created/yeah-fc90e26d51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.makeameme.org%2Fcreated%2Fyeah-fc90e26d51.jpg&h=4d9b01f